democratic front an umbrella organization for antiapartheid 
groups in the power struggle against inkatha 
the agreement condemned violence and established a board to 
review residents complaints of harassment or attacks 
the pact remains in effect but has had limited success some 
witnesses have been afraid to testify and many supporters of the 
