mubarak shamir would propose an egyptian role in getting 
negotiations started between israel and a delegation made up of 
palestinians and representatives from neighboring jordan 
the aim of such talks would be to reach an interim agreement for 
palestinian selfrule in the occupied west bank and gaza strip the 
