ahimeir said shamir would be willing to coax jordan into peace 
talks by agreeing to consider modifications of the ussponsored 
camp david accords signed in 1978 which led to an israeliegyptian 
peace treaty the following year 
we want to get the jordanians into the peace circle we will 
