passersby saw him and took him to a hospital where his recovery 
began 
if id have had to kick it addiction in the streets id have 
been dead for sure warnke said 
he later joined the navy and served one tour of duty in vietnam 
he became a christian and devoted himself to preaching against 
satanism 
